for each recorded track(called a soundClip)  capture pause point relative to song: song.currentTime();

snapshot this value in the soundClips object as "pauseResumePoint";

When song resumes playback soundClip from that value.




write function to add soundClip cue values.
if cue value is less than the current song playback point then don't included 
soundClip in cue loop.

Invoke this function on every play instance.